<item>
            <title>[LU-9198] LFSCK needs to skip verifying layout component without LCME_FL_INIT</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9198</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The PFL 3b phase requires MDS does not instantiate all OST objects at the file create time, and only instantiate necessary objects when the file&apos;s size grows. So that the stripe lovea on the disk could contain layout component with invalid ost_id if its lcme_flags does not contain LCME_FL_INIT flag. LFSCK needs to take care of this kind of composite layout.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
